This is NTRU PEKS full implementation
Some of the files are taken from Thomas Prest's project https://github.com/tprest/Lattice-IBE and some of them are edited for this transformation. 
Therefore, please respect its license and requirements. Shoot me an email at behniar(at)oregonstate.edu if you have any questions.

Dependences: You would need the following libraries
GMP: https://gmplib.org/
NTL: http://www.shoup.net/ntl/
Zmq: http://zeromq.org/intro:get-the-software
and Blake2b:  https://github.com/BLAKE2/libb2 
